==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Horoscopy
<hw>Ho*ros"co*py</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
art or practice of casting horoscopes, or observing the disposition of
the stars, with a view to prediction events.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Aspect of the stars at the time of a person's
birth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Horrendous</ent>⟦br⟧
